cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CC, cs.DL

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language generation and poetry generation specifically. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper uses a genetic algorithm to teach a BRNN model to generate poetry. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper uses a machine learning model to generate poetry. 
- cs.CC (Computational Creativity) is relevant as the paper discusses the FACE theory on computational creativity and justifies the creativity of their method. 
- cs.DL (Deep Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses a BRNN model, which is a type of deep learning model.
